{"tid":1461663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[重po] 沙田警民關係組呀蛇退gp！有關馬鞍山熄街燈","createTime":"2019-08-13T08:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T21:52:16.000Z","uid":186908,"like":175,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"d839c20d94d0cb5cbf0273c63ca8b44a375be84c","tid":1461663,"uid":186908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:52:32.000Z","msg":"繼琴日個post<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[突發] 馬鞍山已經連續熄咗2晚街燈！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459128\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459128</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日係tg見到幾張相 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5SAhjrz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5SAhjrz.jpg&h=aa5abbee&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GBrsGEV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGBrsGEV.jpg&h=78804640&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/88XGL6B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F88XGL6B.jpg&h=e75a6b60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n區議員同呀蛇討論 叫佢地解答<br />\n咁蛇咁串重要退埋group?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重新post過 有巴打話我冇hide 電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e26a7764e0505aec2d49b21f13895f55588236","tid":1461663,"uid":186908,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:54:49.000Z","msg":"呀蛇唔解決問題 竟然走去退group<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e59abce6f7d27e1d9baa688c296f998e94eced","tid":1461663,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T08:54:54.000Z","msg":"[緊急分析]法！不！責！眾！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/145678